Class Receipt

java.lang.Object
  tv.ouya.console.api.Receipt
All Implemented Interfaces:
android.os.Parcelable
public class Receipt
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable

Represents a purchase that successfully occurred in the past. Receipt is a parcelable object used for data-transfer that contains data about the purchase.
